          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1644936706868-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Cut 1 <strong>mozzarella round</strong> per person, then slice the <strong>remaining mozzarella</strong> finely</p><p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the stone</p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong> using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and slice finely lengthways</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1644936709759-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1644936709759-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1644936709759-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
